quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  32,11,Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Malayika w’urupfu ubashinzwe azabatwara ubuzima; hanyuma kwa Nyagasani wanyu ni ho muzasubizwa.”
  32,12,"(Wari kubona bikomeye) iyaba wari kuzabona inkozi z’ibibi zubitse imitwe imbere ya Nyagasani wazo (zigira ziti) “Nyagasani! Twabonye kandi twumvise (ukuri kw’ibyo twahakanaga). Bityo, dusubize (ku isi) dukore ibikorwa byiza. Mu by’ukuri (ubu) twamenye ukuri!”"
  32,13,"N’iyo tuza kubishaka buri wese twari kumuha ukuyoboka kwe, ariko imvugo (y’ibihano) inturutseho ni impamo ko rwose nzuzuza umuriro wa Jahanamu amajini n’abantu bose hamwe"
  32,14,"Ngaho nimwumve (ibihano) kubera kwibagirwa ko muzahura n’uyu munsi wanyu, mu by’ukuri natwe twabibagiwe; kandi nimwumve ibihano bizahoraho kubera ibyo mwajyaga mukora"
  32,15,"Mu by’ukuri abemera amagambo yacu, ni ba bandi baca bugufi bakubama igihe bayibukijwe, basingiza ishimwe n’ikuzo bya Nyagasani wabo, kandi batibona"
  32,16,"Begura imbavu zabo mu buryamo bwabo kugira ngo basabe Nyagasani wabo batinya (ibihano) kandi bizera (ingororano ze), ndetse bakanatanga mu byo twabafunguriye"
  32,17,"Nta n’umwe uzi ibyo bahishiwe biryoheye ijisho, bizaba ingororano z’ibyo bajyaga bakora"
  32,18,Ese uwemera (Allah) ni kimwe n’inkozi y’ibibi? Ntibashobora kureshya (imbere ya Allah)
  32,19,"Ba bandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, bazagororerwa ubuturo mu ijuru nk’izimano ry’ibyo bajyaga bakora"
  32,20,"Naho inkozi z’ibibi, ubuturo bwazo buzaba umuriro; buri uko bazajya bashaka kuwuvamo, bazajya bawusubizwamo maze babwirwe bati “Ngaho nimwumve ibihano by’umuriro mwajyaga muhakana!”"
  32,21,Kandi rwose tuzabasogongeza ku bihano bya hafi (hano ku isi) mbere y’ibihano bihambaye (byo ku munsi w’imperuka) kugira ngo bisubireho
  32,22,Ese ni nde muhemu kurusha uwibutswa amagambo ya Nyagasani we maze akayatera umugongo? Mu by’ukuri tuzihorera ku nkozi z’ibibi
  32,23,"Kandi rwose twahaye Musa igitabo (Tawurati). Bityo, ntuzagire ugushidikanya ko kuzahura na we. Kandi twakigize umuyoboro kuri bene Isiraheli"
  32,24,"Kandi bamwe muri bo (bene Isiraheli) twabagize abayobozi bayobora ku bw’itegeko ryacu, ubwo bihanganaga bakanemera amagambo yacu batayashidikanyaho"
  32,25,Mu by’ukuri Nyagasani wawe ni We uzabakiranura ku munsi w’imperuka mu byo batavugagaho rumwe
  32,26,"Ese ntibibabera ikimenyetso iyo bibajije umubare w’ibisekuru twarimbuye mbere yabo, bakaba banyura mu matongo yabyo? Mu by’ukuri muri ibyo harimo ibimenyetso; ese ntibumva"
  32,27,"Ese ntibabona uko twohereza amazi ku butaka bwumagaye, tukayeresha ibimera bitanga amafunguro ku matungo yabo ndetse na bo ubwabo? Ese ntibabona"
  32,28,"Baranavuga bati “Ese uko kudukiranura kuzaba ryari, niba muri abanyakuri?”"
  32,29,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ku munsi w’urubanza, ukwemera kwa ba bandi bahakanye nta cyo kuzabamarira kandi ntibazarindirizwa (kugira ngo bicuze).”"
  32,30,"Ngaho bitarure ubirengagize unategereze (ibizababaho), mu by’ukuri na bo bategereje (ibizakubaho)"